{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ac31881e7f","title":"要搞一点原子弹氢弹","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"53e2b676dc","index":0,"year":1958,"month":6,"day":21,"articleId":"ac31881e7f"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoxuan-jinghuo","name":"毛泽东选集1-7（静火版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"静火","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/maoxuan-jinghuo.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoxuan-jinghuo":{"comments":[{"id":"8cc710f18b","publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"ac31881e7f","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"这是毛泽东同志在中共中央军委扩大会议上讲话的节录。"}],"contents":[{"id":"1070a45224","type":"title","text":"要搞一点原子弹氢弹","index":0,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"ac31881e7f"},{"id":"6abfb768f2","type":"paragraph","text":"我还是希望搞一点海军，空军搞得强一点。还有那个原子弹，听说就这么大一个东西，没有那个东西，人家就说你不算数。那么好，我们就搞一点。搞一点原子弹，氢弹，我看有十年功夫完全可能。一年不是抓一次，也不是抓两次，也不是抓四次，而是抓它七八次。要下决心，搞尖端技术，赫鲁晓夫不给我们尖端技术极好。如果给了，这个账是很难还的。搞一些人吃饭不干别的，五年不行，十年，总是可以搞出来的。原子弹要有，氢弹也要快。管它什么国，管它什么弹，原子弹，氢弹，我们都要超过。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"ac31881e7f"},{"id":"a35b3da42b","type":"paragraph","text":"西方资产阶级有的，东方无产阶级要有；西方资产阶级没有的，东方无产阶级也要有。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"ac31881e7f"}],"page":{"id":"8901becd79","publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"ac31881e7f","start":1212,"end":1212}}}},"__N_SSG":true}